\c 19
\s Jonatani anoreverera Dhavhidhi kuna Sauro
\p
\v 1 Zvino Sauro wakataura kuna Jonatani mwanakomana wake nekuvaranda vake vose kuti vauraye Dhavhidhi. Asi Jonatani mwanakomana waSauro wakafarira Dhavhidhi kwazvo\x + 18.1.\x*.
\v 2 Jonatani ndokuudza Dhavhidhi achiti: Sauro baba vangu vanotsvaka kukuuraya; naizvozvo zvino, chenjerera hako mangwana, uye ugare pakavanda, uvande.
\v 3 Zvino ini ndichabuda ndokumira parutivi rwababa vangu musango mauri. Zvino ini ndichataurirana nababa vangu pamusoro pako; uye zvandichaona ndichakuudza.
\p
\v 4 Zvino Jonatani wakataura zvakanaka pamusoro paDhavhidhi kuna Sauro baba vake, ndokuti kwavari: Mambo ngaarege kutadzira muranda wake kurwisa Dhavhidhi, nokuti haana kukutadzirai imwi, uye nokuti mabasa ake akarurama zvikuru kwamuri\x + 19.5. Gen.. 42.22.\x*.
\v 5 Nokuti wakaisa upenyu hwake muruoko rwake\x + Vato. 12.3.\x*, ndokuuraya muFirisitia\x + 17.49,50.\x*; Jehovha ndokuitira Israeri wose ruponeso rukuru; makaona uye makafara\x + 11.13. 1 Makor. 11.14.\x*. Zvino munotadzirirei ropa risina mhosva, kuuraya Dhavhidhi pasina chikonzero\x + Mat. 27.4.\x*?
\v 6 Zvino Sauro wakateerera kuinzwi raJonatani, Sauro ndokupika \add achiti\add*: \add Na\add*Jehovha mupenyu, haangaurawi\x + Rut. 3.13.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino Jonatani wakadana Dhavhidhi, Jonatani ndokumuudza mashoko ose awa. Jonatani ndokuunza Dhavhidhi kuna Sauro; zvino akava pamberi pake sazuro \add na\add*marimwezuro\x + 16.21. 18.2,13.\x*.
\s Sauro anoedzazve kuuraya Dhavhidhi
\p
\v 8 Zvino kwakavazve nehondo; Dhavhidhi ndokubuda ndokurwa neVaFirisitia. Zvino wakavarova nekurova kukuru kusvika vatiza pachiso chake.
\v 9 Zvino mweya wakaipa waJehovha wakava pamusoro paSauro agere mumba make, uye pfumo rake riri muruoko rwake\x + Vato. 9.23.\x*; Dhavhidhi ndokuridza neruoko rwake\x + 16.16.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino Sauro wakatsvaka kubaira Dhavhidhi nemumadziro nepfumo; asi wakapukunyuka pakuonekwa naSauro, iye ndokubaira pfumo nemumadziro; Dhavhidhi ndokutiza, ndokupukunyuka usiku uhwo.
\v 11 Zvino Sauro wakatuma nhume kumba kwaDhavhidhi kumurinda nekumuuraya mangwanani. Mikari mukadzi wake ndokuudza Dhavhidhi achiti: Kana ukasaponesa upenyu hwako usiku huno, uchaurawa mangwana\x + Map. 59.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Naizvozvo Mikari wakaburusa Dhavhidhi nepahwindo; zvino akaenda, ndokutiza, ndokupukunyuka\x + Josh. 2.15.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino Mikari wakatora chifananidzo ndokuisa pamubhedha, ndokuisa mutsago wemvere dzembudzi panzvimbo yemusoro wake, ndokufukidza nemucheka.
\v 14 Sauro paakatuma nhume kutora Dhavhidhi, iye ndokuti: Anorwara.
\v 15 Sauro ndokutuma nhume kuzoona Dhavhidhi achiti: Mukwidzei kwandiri ari mumubhedha kuti ndimuuraye.
\v 16 Nhume padzakapinda, zvino tarira, chifananidzo chiri mumubhedha uye mutsago wemvere dzembudzi panzvimbo yemusoro wake.
\v 17 Zvino Sauro wakati kuna Mikari: Wandinyengedzerei kudai, ndokurega muvengi wangu achienda, zvino wapukunyuka? Mikari ndokuti kuna Sauro: Iye wakati kwandiri: Ndirege ndiende; ndichakuurayirei\x + 2 Sam. 2.22.\x*?
\p
\v 18 Saizvozvo Dhavhidhi wakatiza, ndokupukunyuka, ndokusvika kuna Samueri kuRama\x + 1.19.\x*, ndokumuudza zvose Sauro zvaakaita kwaari. Zvino iye naSamueri ndokuenda ndokugara paNaioti.
\v 19 Zvino zvakaudzwa Sauro zvichinzi: Tarirai, Dhavhidhi ari paNaioti paRama\x + 1.19.\x*.
\v 20 Sauro ndokutuma nhume kunotora Dhavhidhi; pavakaona boka revaporofita vachiporofita, naSamueri amire ari mutungamiriri pamusoro pavo, Mweya waMwari ndokuva pamusoro penhume dzaSauro\x + 10.5,6,10.\x*, zvino vakaporofita naivowo\x + Num.. 11.25.\x*.
\v 21 Pakaudzwa Sauro, wakatuma dzimwe nhume; naidzo dzikaporofita saizvozvo. Zvino Sauro wakatumazve nhume rwechitatu, naidzo dzikaporofitawo.
\v 22 Naiye wakaendawo kuRama, ndokusvika patsime guru riri paSeku, ndokubvunza ndokuti: Vana Samueri naDhavhidhi varipi? Zvikanzi: Tarirai, paNaioti paRama\x + 1.19.\x*.
\v 23 Zvino wakaendako kuNaioti paRama\x + 1.19.\x*, zvino Mweya waMwari wakava pamusoro pakewo, akafamba achifamba achiporofita\x + 10.6,10.\x* kusvika asvika paNaioti paRama\x + 1.19.\x*.
\v 24 Naiyewo wakakurura nguvo dzake, naiye wakaporofita pamberi paSamueri\x + 18.10.\x*, ndokurara pasi akashama zuva iro rose neusiku ihwo hwose\x + Isa. 20.2. Mik. 1.8,11. Joh. 21.7. 2 Sam. 6.14,20.\x*. Saka vachiti: Sauro naiye ari pakati pevaporofita here\x + 10.11,12.\x*?
